BoostHub is a DeFi yield aggregator/hub contract that manages staking positions in StakeDAO gauges on behalf of approved strategy contracts. It acts as a central hub that deposits assets into StakeDAO gauges, harvests rewards, distributes them proportionally to stakers, and charges protocol fees. It also manages SDT token locking into vlSDT, voting power delegation via Snapshot, and boost checkpointing for vlBoost.

