BoostHub.sol
Centralization Risk: Owner Can Set Fees Up to 35% Without Timelock
The owner can set fees up to `MAX_TOTAL_FEE_BPS = 3500` (35%) at any time without any timelock or delay. This means the owner can instantly change fees from 0% to 35% on all pools (or specific pools via `setPoolFees`). Since `_harvest` is called on every deposit, a strategy depositing into a pool could face a sudden 35% fee on their next harvest. There is no mechanism for strategies to react to fee changes before they take effect. The `setFees` and `setPoolFees` functions take effect immediately.


